TROY SPEAR UNDERWATER ROBOTICS
ROBOSUB 2023 TECHNICAL DESIGN REPORT (TDR)

This PDF file is a placeholder for the 2023 Technical Design Report for the vehicle: Nautilus.

This document details the inaugural design, engineering, and testing phases of the Nautilus AUV, including:
1. Basic modular PVC frame assembly and manual static buoyancy leveling.
2. Single-camera vision streaming and custom thruster configurations.
3. Arduino Mega controller interface and serial communications.
4. Python script color matching filters for gate target detection.
5. Budgetary bounds and rookie team structure configurations.

Competition Result: RoboSub 2023 Rookie of the Year Award Winner.
